%<a|y>    It is intended for use with \textsf{oxnotes}\slash\textsf{oxnum} and not recommended for this style.
  \item\docValue{comma}
    separates the two with a comma and space, e.g. \enquote{23, 2}.
  \item\docValue{parens}
